{"tid":1113474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鴨寮街放蛇掃鹹碟 檢14萬元貨拘中年漢","createTime":"2019-04-18T02:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T03:31:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6b93a5e6303db00799f143108b8452213244ae05","tid":1113474,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190418/_2019041808231716620.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190418%2F_2019041808231716620.jpg&h=b5cbb007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深水埗警區特別職務隊根據線報及深入調查，於昨午約1時在區內展開反淫褻物品行動，派員喬裝顧客到鴨寮街一店鋪，在鋪內檢獲約5000隻懷疑色情光碟，估計總值約14萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n行動中，警方拘捕一名49歲姓王本地男子，涉嫌「發布淫褻物品」及「管有淫褻物品以供發布用途」，他正被扣查。<br />\n<br />\n警方相信是次行動已成功打擊區內相關活動及三合會非法收入來源。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190418/_2019041808231679022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190418%2F_2019041808231679022.jpg&h=5ba34f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/982187-香港-鴨寮街放蛇掃鹹碟+檢14萬元貨拘中年漢\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F982187-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%B4%A8%E5%AF%AE%E8%A1%97%E6%94%BE%E8%9B%87%E6%8E%83%E9%B9%B9%E7%A2%9F%2B%E6%AA%A214%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B2%A8%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=f795ffaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F982187-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%B4%A8%E5%AF%AE%E8%A1%97%E6%94%BE%E8%9B%87%E6%8E%83%E9%B9%B9%E7%A2%9F%2B%E6%AA%A214%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B2%A8%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2&h=049c2f16\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/982187-香港-鴨寮街放蛇掃鹹碟+檢14萬元貨拘中年漢</a>"},{"pid"